[normal]Written [bold]evidence submitted by the Poverty Practice of the United Nations Development Programme (UNDP) in its capacity as Technical Secretariat of the [bold]United Nations Partnership on the Rights of Persons with Disabilities (UNPRPD)[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Introduction[bold]&#xa0;
