[normal]Human Rights Council Resolution 16/15[bold]. “[bold]Role of international cooperation in support of natio[bold]nal efforts for the realization of the rights of persons with disabilities[bold]”[bold]&#xa0;[bold]The Human Rights Council […] OP8. Welcomes the initiative by the United Nations Development Programme, the Office of the High Commissioner, the Department of Economic and Social A
[normal]ffairs of the United Nations Secretariat and the United Nations Children’s Fund to promote a new multidonor trust fund through the establishment of the United Nations partnership for the rights 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]of persons with disabilities to support the inclusion of the 
[normal]rights of persons with disabilities 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]within the development cooperation programmes of the United Nations system, and 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]encourages States, bilateral and multilateral donors and private donors to give favourable consideration to contributing to it once it has
[normal] been established;
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
